{"tid":1636714,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"支那01居然遣責黑警","createTime":"2019-10-07T19:57:54.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-07T22:00:28.000Z","uid":83689,"like":5,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"f257ba30dd822ecd06b6b679e89a5217f7c26306","tid":1636714,"uid":83689,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T19:57:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3RzBzfb.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3RzBzfb.png&h=8ac7dc91&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n係咪要變東方了<br />\n定又要吹風向<br />\n<br />\n對於警方為何無預警下射藍色水劑，警察公共關係科回覆《香港01》查詢時稱，大批蒙面示威者於旺角警署外聚集，有人挖磚、向警署投擲玻璃樽等。經過多次警告無效，警員展開驅散行動，包括於警署內向外噴射加有顏色水的催淚水劑，又指記者應盡量遠離所有危險點。<br />\n<br />\n然而，警方解釋與《香港01》查詢事項風馬牛不相及，當時警署外並無人挖磚、設路障、塗污警署外牆或向警署投擲玻璃樽，警方噴灑顏色催淚水劑前亦無作出警告。《香港01》新聞部對警方這種干預新聞採訪的行為予以譴責。"},{"pid":"06bcca5d72efc7c1cac365b5a929c0aed382d4f5","tid":1636714,"uid":103230,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T19:58:58.000Z","msg":"琴日俾人踢爆插針連登<br />\n<br />\n有冇咁橋"},{"pid":"5f75e6b0012e90593297332d47ba121837882686","tid":1636714,"uid":33730,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T19:59:14.000Z","msg":"做戲做全套，點都要扮到撐自己記者"},{"pid":"f1555b55ebec32e2205f09bc00b22e83bf98bf0f","tid":1636714,"uid":293667,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T19:59:30.000Z","msg":"傷都唔撚傷啦"},{"pid":"e9259a6d98805e6f6809b172746bf6dc19504e3d","tid":1636714,"uid":134774,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T19:59:44.000Z","msg":"小罵大幫忙"},{"pid":"251756a44f145d7b1cad7181acaa43a7cf8ed074","tid":1636714,"uid":3893,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T20:00:21.000Z","msg":"不嬲扮黃再落你降頭"},{"pid":"baee1f79c0768165e2485c03e3f93d9df636a8e7","tid":1636714,"uid":33848,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T20:02:44.000Z","msg":"比人篤爆上連登吹風咪扮下野<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a2babdc8c4bd566366f948b60c2bf4680999d84f